{"tid":2082301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】今日天氣咁好最適合一家大細去沙灘","createTime":"2020-06-28T02:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T04:07:09.000Z","uid":60539,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb8f8389eead85872407dca64b37c17982fce0a","tid":2082301,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:38:19.000Z","msg":"好多人都唔知今日九龍有遊行<br />\n加上陽光普照<br />\n身邊好多人都打算去沙灘玩<br />\n但有心既話 其實係沙灘都可以有行動<br />\n可以同朋友一齊叫口號呼嘯大家71上街<br />\n又或者見人叫口號可以一齊和應<br />\n<br />\n如果見到身邊既人今日去左玩想屌柒佢港豬<br />\n不如試下Challenge佢一路玩一路叫人71上街<br />\n<br />\n最後想講 抗爭既方法唔只得一種<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力！"},{"pid":"62bc59c2db4ac94816bd0156756c32d8e4273c4e","tid":2082301,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"04dbe828571f249b438bd6d1b1f8be40f62fb250","tid":2082301,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e52301f35f40407db7559b6ba5fb540eb107deb5","tid":2082301,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:40:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2cb51421c02195b69bac7142d14054768ba13783","tid":2082301,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"419955934552db9a3626ad6fc9aa26c1503f07b5","tid":2082301,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8787cbe75c40e216702b928103db4b70eb40f7","tid":2082301,"uid":274417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd85a1f98b6057d37a3d2c6f130ffdeff84666b6","tid":2082301,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf8787cbe75c40e216702b928103db4b70eb40f7","tid":2082301,"uid":274417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"推"},"cited